PILLAR1: ENCAPSULATION:
Implementation of encapsulation : wrap up of data members and member function in single entity for more theory check in copy on date 15 oct.
class Student{
    private:
    string name;
    int age;
    int marks;
    public:
    int getage(){
        cout<<"You are in getage function";
        return this->age;
    }
};

